Reclusa::

"If only there was a way to have them deat each other. We would be rid
of both at once, not having to forsake a single bot on the venture. If
only there was a way to con those goody goodies into believing that
self sacrifice was the only way. Drat, what I wouldn't give to have 5
minutes and be alone with thier CR chambers. Reprogram them and it's
end of the headache for all. Hmmmm, I wonder......" she said the last
more to herself, but very overhearable.
